cctv_analysis.prompt_template:
Analyze this CCTV stream image from location: {location} ({description}). Identify any turnstile failures, gridlocks, physical safety hazards, or heat exhaustion signs. Respond in STRICT JSON matching this schema:
{
  "timestamp": "ISO8601 String",
  "threatLevel": "GREEN | AMBER | RED",
  "analysisSummary": "A clear, 2-3 sentence technical summary of the situation.",
  "detectedElements": [
    {
      "name": "Description of object/situation (e.g. Broken turnstile, dense crowd)",
      "confidence": 0.0-1.0,
      "coordinates": [x, y]
    }
  ],
  "recommendedActions": [
    "Action item 1",
    "Action item 2"
  ]
}

command_parser.prompt_template:
Current Stadium State:
{current_state}

Commander Input: "{user_input}"

Analyze the command and output a JSON response containing:
{
  "understoodCommand": "Brief text of what was understood",
  "targetComponent": "transit | security | medical | maintenance | general",
  "stateUpdates": {
    "field_to_update": "new_value"
  },
  "responseMessage": "A professional feedback message to show on the commander's feed.",
  "suggestedActions": [
    "Next logical step 1",
    "Next logical step 2"
  ]
}

agent_negotiation.negotiation_prompt_template:
Incident Details:
Title: {title}
Category: {category}
Severity: {severity}
Description: {description}

You are playing the role of {agent_name}.
Your goal: {role_goal}
Your priority: {priority}

Previous Agent Dialogue:
{dialogue_history}

Formulate your next response in the conversation. Respond directly as {agent_name}. Offer concrete resources or actions you will execute. Ensure you cooperate with the other agents' suggestions.
